Citation.sTitle: Solubility Investigations in the (NH4)2C2O4-NH4VO3-H2O System from 313.15 to 363.15 K
Citation.sAbstract: The solubility of (NH4)2C2O4-NH4VO3-H2O system has been measured over a temperature range 313.15 K to 363.15 K. On the basis of the results, a solubility diagram has been drawn. Additionally, the densities of the solutions have been measured. From analysis of the solubility data, a separation method for NH4VO3 from (NH4)2C2O4-NH4VO3-H2O system was proposed, involving cooling and salting-out crystallization from (NH4)2C2O4 solution.
